        public static <T> Callback<java.lang.Object,T> iterate(T... values)
        The created Callback iterates over the given values and returns them. If the last element is reached, its value returned for all consecutive calls.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the values
        Parameters:
        values - the values to iterate over
        Returns:
        the given values in order.
